- Yes.

34:04.250 --> 34:05.668
What are you doing here?

34:06.144 --> 34:07.029
I'm the scanner.

34:08.558 --> 34:10.100
Come on, don't feel sorry.

34:10.518 --> 34:12.661
The others guys are at home, doing nothing.

34:14.065 --> 34:17.811
You were such a great cinematographer,
for so many great movies.

34:17.893 --> 34:18.536
Thank you.

34:18.886 --> 34:22.437
You know what... at least I get to work
with the actors, and... light.

34:22.799 --> 34:26.067
I'm lucky... to be able to meet you at work.

34:26.909 --> 34:28.099
Just like the old times.

34:29.038 --> 34:29.850
And,

34:30.817 --> 34:32.782
I also like that I get to tell you to...

34:32.998 --> 34:34.567
take off your beautiful dress.

34:37.920 --> 34:39.677
A changing room down the hall
to your right.

34:42.213 --> 34:43.670
- Good to see you.
- Good to see you.

35:11.213 --> 35:11.904
Chris?

35:15.267 --> 35:16.161
Hello?

35:16.584 --> 35:17.368
Anybody here?

35:17.654 --> 35:18.547
Yeah, I got you, Rob.

35:19.073 --> 35:21.671
Just make yourself comfortable,
we'll start in a minute, OK?

35:33.392 --> 35:34.887
I don't want to miss any of your...

35:35.394 --> 35:37.269
charming expressions here...

35:38.439 --> 35:39.412
Princess.

35:44.320 --> 35:45.602
Now, smile.

35:48.533 --> 35:49.648
Wider.

35:51.134 --> 35:52.119
You're happy.

35:54.831 --> 35:55.530
Happy.

36:01.087 --> 36:02.415
Now, laugh.

36:05.091 --> 36:06.337
Big laugh.

36:08.594 --> 36:09.627
Gimme here your laugh.

36:17.603 --> 36:18.762
Come on, give me a big laugh.

36:25.111 --> 36:26.772
BIG laugh, yeah!

36:31.625 --> 36:33.118
Now, the laughter...

36:34.620 --> 36:35.949
slowly

36:37.540 --> 36:38.916
slowly...

36:40.543 --> 36:41.824
